Class AmqpFeedbackReceivedHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.qpid.proton.engine.BaseHandler
      • com.microsoft.azure.sdk.iot.service.transport.amqps.AmqpFeedbackReceivedHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.qpid.proton.engine.CoreHandler, org.apache.qpid.proton.engine.Handler

    public class AmqpFeedbackReceivedHandler
extends org.apache.qpid.proton.engine.BaseHandler
    Instance of the QPID-Proton-J BaseHandler class to override the events what are needed to handle the receive operation Contains and sets connection parameters (path, port, endpoint) Maintains the layers of AMQP protocol (Link, Session, Connection, Transport) Creates and sets SASL authentication for transport
